{"tid":1838452,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港票房: 王晶/TVB不敵 黃絲電影《新幹線戰士》","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T11:03:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b90d0a4af1aa5172171bb9d8a374b9485548b3","tid":1838452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"中共禁片《返校》香港片主, 疑似係<strong>新映影片(Neofilms)</strong>! &nbsp;而且唔少連登手足都認同新映黃到發金!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1835568/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1835568/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>而家, 新映發行的的日本動畫《劇場版 新幹線戰士 來自未來的神速ALFA-X》首天只上映130場, 但開畫票房竟然略勝TVB出品, 王晶監製的《肥龍過江》!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/73167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F73167&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7b2590f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/73167</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>星王朝發行、谷垣健治執導、甄子丹主演的《肥龍過江》首天於51院映近240場錄得不足四千人次，每場平均人次只有17，推算收入未達25萬名列第五</strong>。《肥》片雖然以甄子丹作賣點，不過觀乎《葉問4完結篇》在港票房未及預期，再加上電影看來已完成一段時間，對於觀眾的吸引力明顯受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n外語電影方面，則以環球發行的《怪醫Ｄ老篤》領先，電影首天安排於58院映近410場錄得逾萬一人次，每場平均人次達27，推算收入達80萬，看來電影主要以男主角羅拔唐尼作為賣點。而兩部動畫首天上映則錄得每場約33至34人次。當中迪士尼發行的《變雀特工》首天於51院映近320場獲逾萬人次捧場，推算收入約65萬，<strong>而新映發行的日本動畫《劇場版 新幹線戰士 來自未來的神速ALFA-X》首天於38院映逾百三場亦獲近4,500人次，推算收入在26萬上下，且看新春假期能否吸納家庭客源。</strong><br />\n<br />\n高先發行，黃子華自編、自導兼自演的<strong>《乜代宗師》首天於58院映近600場以近29,000人次拋離其他對手</strong>，每場平均人次達49，推算數入達二百萬，連同周三晚優先場累積達350萬。《乜》片主要以黃子華作賣點，觀乎前作《棟篤特工》的口碑不弱，故此獲得不少觀眾期待。"},{"pid":"4a7b346b225078a25e76952fbe37099bbddbf373","tid":1838452,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f422053cc53a966cd8fc56c6387e853c687f4b","tid":1838452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3cd4295dafc64921d7a74e308b241d652671be","tid":1838452,"uid":9,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"新映個關公真係做得幾好"},{"pid":"13fb9d7cc08a0a053ebe311a9e596bcc5f734977","tid":1838452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abec605162b05fe63a045aec4eaf9124d2439431","tid":1838452,"uid":191815,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"新幹線戰士係正嘛 一家大細都啱睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c167502971027d31fb47786b97bdc1d27d8653ef","tid":1838452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb17237f68f28ab085ecf09829dc630b93d06cc","tid":1838452,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"變形！新幹線戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96472d7a551936915b16e995d96e706363988ae","tid":1838452,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffd84cb6be8510805b208801d9ec784ed3aab6a","tid":1838452,"uid":193215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e325a437155b76cdbe4dbb3de33c807abd0e0c2","tid":1838452,"uid":6386